title: Spanish Mediterranean villages-built community- Westchase
posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#77149', 'Wrapped in the same earth-tone hues, inviting charm and soft ambience of Spanish Mediterranean villages-built centuries ago, this community presents a modern menu of new world luxuries.', 'The first component of the West 8 master plan, this community provides the personal privacy of a great residential address within an urban utopia that feels more like an old world neighborhood.', 'Enveloped by stately Live Oak trees, this community promises a lifestyle that is, literally, made in the shade.', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Full-service fitness studio', 'Beverage boutique and juice bar', 'Grand fireplace and great room lounge', 'WaterWorks pool, hot tub and showers', 'Wireless business center with PCs', 'Private conference facility', 'Multimedia "home" theater']
